<p>This wonderful Buddha is actually made from quality resin and has been finished in colour and style to look like carved wood. The Buddha has a laughing happy expression on his face and is sat with a wealth toad, an ideal gift meant to bring prosperity and happiness to the owner. The laughing Buddha is known in Japan, as Hotei one of the seven lucky Gods and is based on an eccentric Chinese Zen monk who lived during the Liang Dynasty. Each Buddha comes carefully packed individually in a card box making a lovely gift idea. Dimensions: Height 10cm. Width 17cm. Depth 8cm.</p>